Afterward, I was violated by Suzuki for several hours. He
ejaculated inside me without ever using a condom. After it
was over, I was overwhelmed with strong self-loathing, but
at the same time, I also felt an undeniable sense of
satisfaction.
"...A dream? That was quite... a scary dream..."

"Ah... She's streaming again today... I better hurry up...
and watch..."

"Haah... Haah... A dream...?... Hahaha, that's right!
There's no way Makoto would say something like that to
me...!"

"That's right... Makoto would forgive everything...! Even
the fact that I masturbated during your stream...!"

As Makoto collapsed, it seemed she also dragged the camera
down with her. The screen shook and Makoto's figure
disappeared, but the stream was still ongoing. I was about
to leave my seat, thinking that today's show must surely be
over, when I overheard the men's conversation and stopped in
my tracks.

"Hahahahaha!! That was an incredible defecation show!! Quite
the spectacle!! I almost felt like giving a round of
applause!!"

"Look at that anus!! It seems to be completely destroyed
this time!! From now on, she'll never be able to go without
diapers!!"

"However, with this, she's finally become useless! What
shall we do? Shall we keep this woman around for a bit
longer?"

"Nah, it's time to dump her! Oh! I know the perfect place to
dispose of her!"

"What's that...? Pfft!! That place is indeed perfect!! Then,
shall we transport her while she's still unconscious?!"

"This marks the end of the stream! Thank you for everything,
Makoto-chan! From now on, you'll be entertaining various
people in a new land!!"

"These guys... they're really going to abandon Makoto... I
knew it would come to this someday... but..."

I knew it, but I wasn't at all prepared to face that
reality. When the moment came, my chest tightened so much it
felt like my heart would stop. As I writhed in agony, a
location appeared on the monitor.

It seems those men had exposed the intended dumping site for
Makoto on the net. Looking closely at the displayed map, it
was the next town over. The neighboring town was infamous
for its poor public safety, a den of evil.

"I see... Makoto is going to be abandoned in the neighboring
town... Makoto is in the neighboring town..."

The location I had so desperately wanted to know about
Makoto was easily revealed. The neighboring town was far,
but not impossibly so. I pondered for a while and then
quietly looked up at the ceiling.

"Do I... still want to save Makoto...? After all this... do
I still..."

Suddenly, the nightmare I had seen the other day resurfaced
in my mind. If I'm not serious about saving her, it won't
work out. That's right. I've made excuses to myself many
times and didn't save Makoto.

"Then it's fine... Forget about Makoto... I'm just a loser
and a coward... That would be much easier..."

But no matter how much it hurt, I couldn't forget. The days
filled with memories of spending time with Makoto still
shone brightly within me. I did nothing, but I want to
believe that my desire to save Makoto was genuine.

"Makoto said it in my dream. If just thinking could change
reality, no one would have any trouble... So then... I have
to take action this time..."

I staggered to my feet and left the room without anyone
noticing. Then, without taking anything with me and barely
using my head, I started walking aimlessly towards the
neighboring town. At this rate, it might take days to get
there.

Still, I walked. It was all I could do. Both Makoto and I
had fallen as far as we could. But it wasn't over yet, and I
continued on with a sliver of hope in my heart.
